(415, 208, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:2:{i:0;a:4:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:2158:"<h1>Residential Opportunity Fund Takes Flight</h1>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Los Angeles, January 2013 – Wealth management provider, Camden Capital, announced the initial closing of the Camden Residential Opportunity Fund. The fund makes opportunistic investments in single-family, foreclosed properties located in select markets throughout California.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Wedgewood Enterprises, the underlying portfolio manager of the fund, is a privately-held, California-based company that has been profitable since its inception in 1985. Its core business is the purchase, rehabilitation and resale of foreclosed properties.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">This offering is the latest example of Camden’s ability to provide its high-net worth clients unique access to exclusive investment products. The fund provides a preferred quarterly return along with a distribution of final profits upon liquidation. Fund administration is handled by JD Clark, while Rothstein Kass is providing the Audit and Tax Services. The fund was advised by Stradley Ronon Stevens &amp; Young, LLP.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Camden’s Founder and CEO, John Krambeer, stated, “Our client-base is extremely enthusiastic about this offering. Today we are providing direct access to an investment vehicle not offered by other firms. The fund is being managed by a well-established organization that has a historic track record while the fund is also uniquely structured to minimize downside risk for our investors.”</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Camden Capital provides unbiased investment advice and legacy planning to prominent high net worth individuals, families, business owners and entrepreneurs. With a focus on developing long-term relationships, the firm has grown extensively through client referral. Camden’s relentless commitment to achieving its clients’ objectives, exclusive investment platform and consolidated performance and tax reporting are at the core of its value proposition.</p>\n\n<a class="btn" title="BACK TO RECOGNITION" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/recognition/">BACK TO RECOGNITION</a>";s:6:"filter";s:1:"1";s:4:"info";a:4:{s:4:"grid";s:1:"0";s:4:"cell";s:1:"0";s:2:"id";s:1:"0";s:5:"class";s:14:"WP_Widget_Text";}}i:1;a:4:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:162:"\n<div class="post-sidebar">\n<br />\n<img class="photo" src="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/residential-opportunity-fund.jpg"/>\n</div>";s:6:"filter";s:0:"";s:4:"info";a:4:{s:4:"grid";s:1:"0";s:4:"cell";s:1:"1";s:2:"id";s:1:"1";s:5:"class";s:14:"WP_Widget_Text";}}}s:5:"grids";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:"cells";s:1:"2";}}s:10:"grid_cells";a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:6:"weight";s:17:"0.799752781211372";s:4:"grid";s:1:"0";}i:1;a:2:{s:6:"weight";s:19:"0.20024721878862795";s:4:"grid";s:1:"0";}}}'),
