(422, 214, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:2:{i:0;a:4:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:2043:"<h1>Rich P. Bursek Joins as Partner​</h1>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Palm Beach, October 2012 – Camden Capital announces the addition of Rich P. Bursek as Partner. Prior to his arrival at Camden, Mr. Bursek was the Chief Operating Officer of a wealth management and trust business with offices throughout Florida. Mr. Bursek has a 20-year track record of working with leading financial services firms and he has led interactive strategy and marketing teams for Fortune 500 companies including AT&amp;T, Bank of America, The Coca-Cola Company and Ford Motor Company.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Mr. Bursek is responsible for corporate development and the national expansion of the firm. He leads the discovery and successful integration of professionals who passionately share the company’s investment philosophy, client centric approach and relentless drive to exceed expectations. Responsibilities also include branding, marketing, public relations, client communications and the ongoing development of the firm’s investment product offering.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">“The addition of Mr. Bursek strengthens Camden’s management team and enhances our ability to grow our practice,” stated CEO and Founder, John Krambeer. “Rich has the unique understanding of the high-net worth wealth management space and he has a proven track record of executing a well defined growth strategy.”</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Camden Capital provides unbiased investment advice and legacy planning to prominent high net worth individuals, families, business owners and entrepreneurs. With a focus on developing long-term relationships, the firm has grown extensively through client referral. Camden’s relentless commitment to achieving its clients’ objectives, exclusive investment platform and consolidated performance and tax reporting are at the core of its value proposition.<