(13, 1, '2014-06-19 16:46:13', '2014-06-19 16:46:13', '<h2>AN INDEPENDENT, REGISTERED INVESTMENT ADVISORY FIRM THAT PROVIDES UNBIASED INVESTMENT ADVICE AND LEGACY PLANNING FOR THE HIGH NET WORTH.</h2>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We establish long-term relationships with clients built on a foundation of trust and personal service by creating solutions individually tailored to meet their complex needs.We are a fee-based only model and we custody assets at third party custodians.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our relentless commitment to achieving our clients'' objectives, exclusive investment access and consolidated performance and tax reporting are at the core of our value proposition.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We understand the needs of our clients and our track record proves it. We have grown our business primarily through referrals along with exceptional client retention.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="About" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/about/">OVERVIEW</a></p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Leadership" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/about/leadership/">LEADERSHIP</a></p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/about/board/">BOARD</a></p>\n\n"Our mission is to improve the\nfinancial quality and overall peace of mind of our clients."Mark H. Udis, Partner', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2014-06-27 15:27:03', '2014-06-27 15:27:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/www/camdencapital/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
