(19, 1, '2014-06-19 16:46:54', '2014-06-19 16:46:54', '<h2>A RELENTLESS COMMITMENT TO ACHIEVING OUR CLIENTS'' OBJECTIVES, INVESTMENT ACCESS AND CONSOLIDATED REPORTING ARE AT THE CORE OF OUR VALUE PROPOSITION.</h2>\n\n</p>\n<p>Our wealth managment philosophy is driven by four core\ncomponents that surround every interaction with our clients:</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a title="About" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/">OVERVIEW</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a title="Leadership" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/holistic-planning/">HOLISTIC PLANNING</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/financial-insight/">FINANCIAL INSIGHT</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">INVESTMENT ACCESS</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/relentless-service/">RELENTLESS SERVICE</a>\n</p>\n\n"Honesty, integrity, authenticity and expertise are at the heart of the client experience."Rich P. Bursek, Partner\n\n<p style="text-align: justify"><a title="Holistic Planning" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/holistic-planning/">HOLISTIC PLANNING</a></p>\n<p>\nComprehensive holistic wealth management and life planning focused on wealth preservation for generations to follow. Unbiased and conflict-free investment strategies utilizing third-party, institutional custodians.\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify"><a href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/financial-insight/">FINANCIAL INSIGHT</a></p>\n<p>\nConsolidated performance and tax reporting including investments managed by others. Performance is reported on gross and net of fees along with detailed tax information that may also be provided to your designated CPA.\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify"><a href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">INVESTMENT ACCESS</a></p><p>\nUnbiased access to institutional level investments including world class third-party managers, exclusive private equity funds, alternative investments and asset based lending.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify"><a href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">RELENTLESS SERVICE</a></p><p>\nWe understand your needs and our track record proves it. We have grown our business through referrals and exceptional client retention.</p>', 'Aproach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aproach', '', '', '2014-06-27 20:56:47', '2014-06-27 20:56:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/www/camdencapital/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
