(111, 1, '2014-06-26 21:57:20', '2014-06-26 21:57:20', '<h2>INDUSTRY LEADING WEALTH MANAGERS AND PRIVATE EQUITY FUNDS NOT READILY ACCESSIBLE TO THE MASS AFFLUENT.</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our focus on the high- and ultra-high net worth provides direct access to exclusive third-party managers and unique investment products not easily accessible to the mass affluent. We excel at developing customized, traditional and tax efficient strategies utilizing:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Institutional-level third-party managers</li>\r\n	<li>Traditional equities and fixed income</li>\r\n	<li>Separately managed accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Unified managed accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Private equity funds</li>\r\n	<li>Alternative investments</li>\r\n	<li>Asset-based lending</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTHIRD-PARTY MANAGERS\r\nWe select and monitor industry leading investment managers who have an exceptional pedigree by demonstrating historic out-performance relative to their index, consistently manage downside risk, have proper risk control procedures in place and whose investment philosophies are aligned with ours.\r\n\r\nManagers selected are world-class experts in their sector. They are highly accessible, attentive and responsive to the needs of prominent high-net worth families while understanding the importance of remaining discreet. The impressive character and ongoing achievements of our wealth managers sets us apart from our peers.\r\n\r\nSelected wealth managers must demonstrate the following criteria:\r\nExceptional pedigree\r\nHistoric out-performance track records relative to their index\r\nConsistent downside risk management\r\nModest fund size and disciplined approach\r\nInternal risk control procedures and proper staffing\r\nAligned investment philosophies\r\nPRIVATE EQUITY: CAMDEN OPPORTUNITY FUNDS\r\nWhile private investment offerings are normally reserved for institutional investors, Camden Opportunity Funds was created to provide access to unique 