(177, 1, '2014-06-27 21:06:51', '2014-06-27 21:06:51', '<h2>CONSOLIDATED PERFORMANCE AND TAX REPORTING ON ASSETS INCLUDING THOSE MANAGED BY THIRD-PARTY INSTITUTIONS.</h2>\n\n<p>We report on investments, even those we are not managing. Performance is shown on a relative and absolute basis, both before and after the effect of cash flows, in order to provide maximum transparency. Manager performance is tracked against a large supply of relevant benchmarks, broad-market indices and their peers.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="About" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/">OVERVIEW</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Leadership" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/holistic-planning/">HOLISTIC PLANNING</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/financial-insight/">FINANCIAL INSIGHT</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">INVESTMENT ACCESS</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/relentless-service/">RELENTLESS SERVICE</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">We meet with clients on a quarterly basis to review performance and learn about new developments that may require a change in investment strategy. Year-to-date, quarterly and trailing twelve month tax information allows you to have a clear understanding of your tax situation.\n\nProviding you with the most up-to-date information allows us to make intelligent and informed decisions while planning accordingly. We provide this information to you and your designated CPA.</p>', 'Financial Insight', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 21:06:51', '2014-06-27 21:06:51', '', 23, 'http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(178, 1, '2014-06-27 21:08:35', '2014-06-27 21:08:35', '<h2>INDUSTRY LEADING WEALTH MANAGERS AND PRIVATE EQUITY FUNDS NOT READILY ACCESSIBLE TO THE MASS AFFLUENT.</h2>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">Our focus on the high- and ultra-high net worth provides direct access to exclusive third-party managers and unique investment products not easily accessible to the mass affluent. We excel at developing customized, traditional and tax efficient strategies utilizing:</p>\n\nInstitutional-level third-party managers\nTraditional equities and fixed income\nSeparately managed accounts\nUnified managed accounts\nPrivate equity funds\nAlternative investments\nAsset-based lending\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="About" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/">OVERVIEW</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Leadership" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/holistic-planning/">HOLISTIC PLANNING</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/financial-insight/">FINANCIAL INSIGHT</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">INVESTMENT ACCESS</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/relentless-service/">RELENTLESS SERVICE</a>\n</p>\n\n<h3>THIRD-PARTY MANAGERS</h3>\n<p style="text-align: justify">We select and monitor industry leading investment managers who have an exceptional pedigree by demonstrating historic out-performance relative to their index, consistently manage downside risk, have proper risk control procedures in place and whose investment philosophies are aligned with ours.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Managers selected are world-class experts in their sector. They are highly accessible, attentive and responsive to the needs of prominent high-net worth families while understanding the importance of remaining discreet. The impressive character and ongoing achievements of our wealth managers sets us apart from our peers.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Selected wealth managers must demonstrate the following criteria:</p>\n\nExceptional pedigree\nHistoric out-performance track records relative to their index\nConsistent downside risk management\nModest fund size and disciplined approach\nInternal risk control procedures and proper staffing\nAligned investment philosophies\n\n<h3>PRIVATE EQUITY: CAMDEN OPPORTUNITY FUNDS</h3>\n<p style="text-align: justify">While private investment offerings are normally reserved for institutional investors, Camden Opportunity Funds was created to provide access to unique investment opportunities that may provide superior yield and appreciation results, have relative short and intermediate illiquidity periods and do not encompass a separate layer of fees.</p>\n\n<h3>ALTERNATIVE INVESTMENTS</h3>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Our investment recommendations may possess a range of alternative investments such as private equity, real estate, commodities and hedge funds. In today’s interest rate environment, alternatives have grown in popularity as investment managers have struggled with the rising price of traditional equities and fixed income products with minimum yield. We are dedicated to identifying alternative asset managers who subscribe to the philosophy of protecting clients’ assets when utilized as a satellite offering to the overall core position.</p>\n\n<h3>ASSET-BASED LENDING</h3>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Camden Capital competitively shops lending rates from multiple institutions. This bidding process allows us to obtain pricing below what most clients achieve on their own and removes the burden from the client. We also offer aggressive margin lending rates on investable assets through our third-party custodians.</p>', 'Investment Access', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 21:08:35', '2014-06-27 21:08:35', '', 25, 'http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(179, 1, '2014-06-27 21:09:43', '2014-06-27 21:09:43', '<h2>WE HAVE GROWN OUR BUSINESS THROUGH REFERRALS AND\nEXCEPTIONAL CLIENT RETENTION.</h2>\n\n<p>Independently owned, our allegiance is to our clients. Our independence allows us to remain focused on building a premier financial service organization that meets the complex and sophisticated needs of the high net worth.</p>\n<p>We are focused on growing our business so we can continue to meet the evolving and dynamic needs of our sophisticated client base. The Camden Capital team is comprised of experienced and dedicated investment professionals. Each team member is focused on providing their clients with the highest level of service.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="About" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/">OVERVIEW</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Leadership" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/holistic-planning/">HOLISTIC PLANNING</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/financial-insight/">FINANCIAL INSIGHT</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/investment-access/">INVESTMENT ACCESS</a>\n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center">\n<a title="Board" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/aproach/relentless-service/">RELENTLESS SERVICE</a>\n</p>', 'Relentless Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 21:09:43', '2014-06-27 21:09:43', '', 27, 'http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
