(185, 1, '2014-06-27 21:23:18', '2014-06-27 21:23:18', '<h1>CEO Recognized as Top Advisor by Barron''s</h1>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">Los Angeles, February 2014 – CEO and Founder, John M. Krambeer was recently distinguished by Barron’s as one of America’s Top Financial Advisors. The financial publication recognizes financial advisors that represent the top one percent of advisors who have substantial and well-managed practices located in the United States. Assets under management, quality of practices and operating an efficient business model were the lead criteria.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">"This recognition speaks volumes about our practice, our loyal client base and the dedicated, world-class professionals of Camden Capital,” stated Mr. Krambeer. “Camden Capital was founded to provide a holistic and conflict-free approach to wealth management and legacy planning for prominent high net worth families, business owners and entrepreneurs. The firm prides itself on being established one client, and one employee, at a time. It is rewarding to know our disciplined approach and unbiased investment philosophy led to this recognition.”</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">Over the past twelve months, Camden Capital has been building upon its core foundation and expanding its boutique offering throughout the country. It recently opened an office in North Palm Beach, Florida and added leading professionals to support its client base. Its independent structure, conflict-free investment platform and underlying fiduciary duty differentiate it from a majority of the national firms and have been contributors to its success.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify">Camden Capital provides unbiased investment advice and legacy planning to high and ultra-high net worth individuals and families. With a focus on developing long-term relationships with its clients, the firm has grown exclusively through referrals. Camden’s relentless commitment to achieving its clients’ objectives, exclusive investment access and consolidated performance and tax reporting are at the core of its value proposition.</p>\n\n<a class="btn" title="BACK TO RECOGNITION" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/recognition/">BACK TO RECOGNITION</a>\n\n<img class="photo" src="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/John-Krambeer.jpg" />', 'Barrons Top Advisor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-27 21:23:18', '2014-06-27 21:23:18', '', 125, 'http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/125-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
