(196, 1, '2014-06-27 21:38:51', '2014-06-27 21:38:51', '<h1>13th Fastest Growing RIA Firm​</h1>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Los Angeles, July 2013 – Camden Capital was recently named the 13th Fastest Growing Registered Investment Advisory Firm by Financial Advisor Magazine.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify">The high net worth wealth management firm attributes its success to providing superior client service and world-class investment access. Camden Capital’s Founder &amp; CEO, John Krambeer, states, “We thank our clients and our staff for this recognition. We continue to grow our business organically through referrals and the addition of seasoned wealth management professionals who understand the distinct needs of our clients. This recognition is a testament to our model, our loyal clients and staff.”</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Earlier this year, Camden Capital opened an office in North Palm Beach, Florida, giving the firm a presence in two of the country’s most affluent markets. Camden’s ability to offer access to exclusive investment products through wealth management professionals throughout the country continues to set it apart.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify">Camden Capital provides unbiased investment advice and legacy planning to prominent high net worth individuals, families, business owners and entrepreneurs. With a focus on developing long-term relationships, the firm has grown extensively through client referral. Camden’s relentless commitment to achieving its clients’ objectives, exclusive investment platform and consolidated performance and tax reporting are at the core of its value proposition.</p>\n<p><a class="btn" title="BACK TO RECOGNITION" href="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/recognition/">BACK TO RECOGNITION</a></p>\n\n<img class="photo" src="http://192.168.1.86/camdencapital/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/FA.jpg" />', 'Fastest Growing Ria', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fastest-growing-ria', '', '', '2014-06-27 21:41:21